1. Created a new directory called 0x03-sass_scss inside the alx-intermediate-frontend repository.

2. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using NVM by running:
   $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
   $ nvm install 20.16
   $ nvm use 20.16

3. Installed SASS globally using npm:
   $ npm install sass -v 3.7.4

4. Installed SASS locally for specific projects:
   $ npm install sass --save-dev

4. Verified SASS installation by running:
   $ sass --version
